{"tid":2529473,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"每週飲食記錄  滷水鵝、鹹蛋蝦炒飯","createTime":"2021-05-13T18:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T19:41:00.000Z","uid":62277,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"70c72a8e14390fdc6b3dec3347958a94cbbca996","tid":2529473,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T18:41:47.000Z","msg":"自問唔識寫食評<br />\n對各種食物研究亦唔深<br />\n無打算要得到人認同係識食<br />\n但每日都會瘋狂揾美食去彌補自己對生活既不滿<br />\n<br />\n本身無乜朋友，無人可以同我傾食野<br />\n所以想喺度隨意post下圖鳩up幾句<br />\n同人接觸下等自己唔好咁封閉<br />\n希望從中得到一些食野心得/揾食好路數<br />\n就算巴打對我既口味有批評<br />\n都會好樂意接受<br />\n因為有批評先會有進步<br />\n<br />\n計劃每星期都開一次post<br />\n講一、兩餐食過既野<br />\n希望今次可以堅持耐啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8cb56da016852f01584db38e0f83f61b3d0069","tid":2529473,"uid":62277,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T18:53:15.000Z","msg":"一直都鍾意燒鵝多過滷水鵝<br />\n第一次食到滿意既滷水汁<br />\n入味得嚟清香，酒味重<br />\n鵝肉質都ok,胸位都唔鞋<br />\n以後會多啲揾滷水鵝食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ46nZPnVJjesRRqcjA2P6EGrLXMppzVBuJumbFVoG1Eu?filename=q6hGQjq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6hGQjq.jpg&h=ab0eb5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店名：尚興潮州飯店"},{"pid":"3db606ee6b3fa8f758346abbc6b7236589e0c58f","tid":2529473,"uid":62277,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T19:11:52.000Z","msg":"呢間酒樓有好多特色小菜<br />\n我第一次嚟lunch只係叫咗碟炒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鹹蛋蝦炒飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY6tbDwxab2vsAhCnd1gapcvjP9GncGzfLRSgBqBnXuiS?filename=k0mcW3G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0mcW3G.jpg&h=81c5da3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感覺唔錯<br />\n每一啖都有鹹蛋香<br />\n飯夠乾身、粒粒分明<br />\n蝦亦鮮<br />\n如果多啲蔥更加好<br />\n最後一個人啃唔落一碟，打包做晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n始終酒樓既炒飯一般嚟講比茶記可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店名：楓林小館"},{"pid":"000ed066017d45c14260c70c3f94f9e6e205e152","tid":2529473,"uid":127044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T19:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af83729133598118ee4873fd4b719a3e78706408","tid":2529473,"uid":258345,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T22:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ac405bb7f0c462c9518922ead5aec909d4f121","tid":2529473,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T22:16:58.000Z","msg":"酒樓、飯店嘅炒飯陣香味鑊氣茶記真係好少有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乾身粒粒分明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebaf862a048c549da0b74d5417281c5fc13b8a2","tid":2529473,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e8cb56da016852f01584db38e0f83f61b3d0069","tid":2529473,"uid":62277,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T18:53:15.000Z","msg":"一直都鍾意燒鵝多過滷水鵝<br />\n第一次食到滿意既滷水汁<br />\n入味得嚟清香，酒味重<br />\n鵝肉質都ok,胸位都唔鞋<br />\n以後會多啲揾滷水鵝食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6hGQjq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6hGQjq.jpg&h=ab0eb5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店名：尚興潮州飯店"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T22:45:41.000Z","msg":"加檸檬同蜜糖一流  <br />\n襯上甜酸鹼味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110d00bbf44913e94fdd8544f092c94b9d3d37c8","tid":2529473,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T00:48:39.000Z","msg":"支持bbg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkg